title: Ranked Queue down
body:
Hey guys is ranked queue down at the moment? I can't see it in my available game modes?
I am level 30, and I have ranked. I'm 1 win shy of promotion, so really want that game haha

replies.body: Never mind it's back up now - looks like it had something to do with some outage going on by some 3rd party hardware ISP's were using!
